scalability is the 4th step of the system design process.

what are system design questions?
examples are:
- design a URL shortening service like bit.ly
- implement a web search engine
- design a client-server application which allows people to play chess with one another.

*A system can be built in different ways!
WHAT IS IMPORTANT IS TO BE ABLE TO JUSTIFY MY IDEAS.
